-- Michigan Couple Stole GM Secrets for Chinese Company, U.S Says
-- B y   M a r g a r e t   C r o n i n   F i s k   a n d   S t e v e   R a p h a e l
-- 2012-11-05T15:43:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-05/michigan-couple-stole-gm-secrets-for-chinese-company-u-s-says.html
A former  General Motors Co. (GM)  engineer
and her husband stole  trade secrets  related to hybrid car
technology from the automaker to use in developing such vehicles
in China, a U.S. prosecutor said at the beginning of trial.  To contact the reporter on this story:
